parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbag warning light flickers or turns off intermittently
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty occupant restraint module can cause the airbag warning light to come on, indicating a potential problem with the airbag system, which can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbag warning light flickers or turns off intermittently
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can leave vehicles with potentially life-threatening safety issues on the road, putting drivers and passengers at risk.
symptoms: dealerships are unable to perform recall repairs
owners are left waiting for extended periods for repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Transmission Control Module (TCM) can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, refuse to shift gears, or experience sudden acceleration, leading to loss of control, accidents, or strandings.

The mechanical failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, refuse to shift gears, or experience sudden acceleration, leading to loss of control, accidents, or strandings.
Electronic control issues with the transmission can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to loss of control, accidents, or strandings.

The failure of the transmission shifting system can cause the gear shift to become stuck in park, making it difficult or impossible to operate the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shift is stuck in park

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sun visor can cause it to drop randomly while driving, blocking the view through the windshield, which can lead to accidents or distractions.
symptoms: The sun visor drops randomly while driving
the sun visor does not stay up or forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine White Smoke and Air Conditioning Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine and air conditioning system can cause white smoke to emit from the engine, and the air conditioning to stop blowing cold air, which can lead to engine damage and discomfort.

the air conditioning stops blowing cold air.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the window can cause distractions, injuries, and damage to the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: The window shatters suddenly without any apparent cause
no damage to the exterior or interior of the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a burning smell, white smoke, and potentially lead to an electrical fire, which can be a safety hazard.
symptoms: White smoke emitted from the engine area

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leaving the driver stranded.
